title: Team Slogans with Conor Orr
itunes:title: Team Slogans with Conor Orr
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the NFL starting with why the Jets can't have nice things. Ricky Hollywood surprises the boys with a surprise Saints guest and Conor Orr stops by to go through the 2021 team slogans. We close the show with a flashback to the first time Wess talked about his Bengals divorce dossier.
